## Fix Patterns

### Object Creation in useFrame
Pre-allocate colors at component scope:
```tsx
const targetDarkColor = new THREE.Color("#4c1d95");
const targetLightColor = new THREE.Color("#7c3aed");
```

### Stale Ref Cleanup
Capture ref before cleanup:
```tsx
useEffect(() => {
  const mesh = meshRef.current;
  return () => {
    if (mesh) mesh.geometry.dispose();
  };
}, []);
```

### Geometry Disposal
Add cleanup effect for useMemo geometries:
```tsx
useEffect(() => {
  return () => geometry.dispose();
}, [geometry]);
```

### Environment Deduplication
Load once in Scene.tsx, pass via props or context.
